                    <span>Do NOT order this book from Amazon. I placed an order for this book as a gift on February 9th and after numberous unaccounted for delays on Amazon's part the book now has an estimated delivery of April 9th. That's 2 whole months after my order was placed! It has been pushed back 4 times now, and each time I wasn't notified until 2 days AFTER it was supposed to ship. Now, every single holiday I would have had the opportunity to give this gift to the intended receiver has past or will be past by April 9th. They really should have it listed as out of stock. I'm so upset with Amazon's service lately, every package I've ordered in the past month and a half has been late.  If you really want this book go buy it from a respectable company with prompt service. Amazon has clearly mislead its customers recently. After 4 years of being a devoted customer, I will no longer be using Amazon anymore. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Full of factual errors</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
