                    </div>
                    <span>Kahney is a hack, sadly, and while Mac fanatics may love a world in which Apple can do no wrong, they will be ill-served by this bomb.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">By MacPeople, about Mac's and for MacLovers</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>7</span>
                      /
                      <span>7</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
